{
  "title": "Kiapatatubitubi",
  "titleCh": "婚禮前淚別情人",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "魯凱族很懂哭的藝術，無論是喜，還是哀，都知道如何用哭聲表達感受。尤其婦女們，必定懂得哭，從荳蔻年華的少女便學習如何哭出心中的哭詞，這在原住民族群是特別不一樣，因此很被認為會哭的族群。對於往生者的哭是「悼念的哭」；結婚是「哭別過去的男女情人、朋友」。",
      "ab": "Malrigili ki atubiane kay Ngudradrekay, adravane ka matiakiragay, ka matiathalithi, wathingale tuutubi si putaluvaivay ku yakay ki kidremedreme, saniange kay labaibay, tarawathingale tubi, lasingikay lukatawvaylekete kibuubulru kicaucaucakuane ku lrikasaiyaiya ku vaga lutubi, muakalrivili ki lakacalrisilrisiane, suadalepe “Taratubi kay Ngudradrekay” kiiya. Kikay watubi ki wapacay “sialringaw” laiya; kikay marudrarudrange “kiapatatubi” amia.",
